Create a new vector `ans`.

Now, we can simply do :

`ans[0] = nums[0]`

and now, 

we run a loop till end of vector, and use the following formula for populating vactor `ans` :

> ans[i] = ans[i - 1] + nums[i]

just note to start the loop from `i = 1`.

