	 prefixSum[i] = prefixSum[i - 1] + nums[i], it means,
	 prefixSum[3] = prefixSum[3 - 1] + nums[3],
	 prefixSum[3] = prefixSum[2] + nums[3] // calculate answers;
	 prefixSum[3] = 6 + 4;
	 prefixSum[3] = 10;
	 prefixSum array = {1, 3, 6, 10}

	 Hope you get the idea behind Prefix Sum. 💕

